<div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-3">
        <div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-image hide-panel-body">
            <img src="/dmubanner1.jpg" class="panel-image-preview">
          </div>
          <div class="panel-footer">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-2"><img src="\avatar1.png" height="50px" width="50px" class="rounded-img home-avatar"></div>
                <div class="col-sm-10"><h4 style="text-align: center;"><%= current_user.username %></h4></div>
                <div class="col-sm-12" style="margin-top: 10px;">
                  <div class="col-sm-6" style="font-size: 80%; opacity: 0.7;">POSTS<br>
                    <h6 style="color: #0084B4; font-size: 200%;"><%= current_user.posts.count %></h6>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-sm-6" style="font-size: 80%; opacity: 0.7;">FOLLOWERS<br>
                    <h6 style="color: #0084B4; font-size: 200%;"><%= current_user.followers.count %></h6>
                  </div>
                </div>
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-body">


     <h5 style="color: grey; font-size: 130%;">Home Page</h5>
        <span style="color: darkblue;">What to do</span><br>
        <p> Within the home page you can view post messages of users that are following you, by clicking on a user name you will be
          able to view thier profile. You can aslo post a message from here as well, all messages that are post will redirect you to the
          explore page to be seen along with all the users that have posted.
        </p>

        <span style="color: darkblue;">Wanna Get In Contact</span><br>
        <p> To get in contact with use depending on the situation, we are always avialable to help. You can also view the about page which will give
        the university location and how to get in contact with us. But if that is not enough, the link bottow will direct you to the official information
        regarding contacting the right person that you need.</p>
        <a href="http://www.dmu.ac.uk/General/Contact-us.aspx?gclid=CjwKCAjw8r_XBRBkEiwAjWGLlGb5MPeQcLB8-D-yfraxNLt5STsoqS6IFdcWCCu4My4o6p5aC3NRWhoC8e0QAvD_BwE">Contact Us?</a><br>







          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-6">
        <%= render '/postcomponents/post_form' %><br><br>

        <% for @p in @post %>
        <div class="panel panel-default post-panel">
          <div class="panel-body row">

            <div class="col-sm-1">
              <img src="\avatar1.png" class="rounded-img" height="50px" width="50px"></img>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-11">
              <p class="post-title"><span class="post-owner"><a href="/user/<%= User.find(@p.user_id).username %>"><%= User.find(@p.user_id).username %></a></span> <span class="post-creation">- <%= @p.created_at.to_formatted_s(:short) %></span></p>
              <p class="post-content"><%= @p.content %></p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <% end %>
    </div>
    <div class="col-xs-3">
        <div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-body">
            <p style="opacity: 0.5; font-size: 90%;">Â© 2018 De Montfort University Social Media Page  About: Helping Student better take control of thier uni experince and to make friends easily when needed</p>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
